## ⚠️ Common Errors & Fixes

| Error | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| Output directory exists | `hdfs dfs -rm -r /user/hadoop/wordcount/output` |
| Hadoop not started | Run `start-dfs.sh` again |
| Java not found | Run `java -version` to check |
| Permission denied | Run `chmod +x start-dfs.sh` |

